    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Auripertus/Toto">Auriperto</name>, que Toto
                            vocatur</persName>, filio <persName>quondam <name ref="Martinus"
                                >Martini</name></persName> riceve da <persName ref="#people/214"
                            key="#Bishops">Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane
                        ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario
                        nomine (…), casa et res illa in loco et finibus a <placeName
                            ref="#places/471">Luniano, ubi dicitur a Colle</placeName>, pertenentes
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> vestre <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/70" key="#Churches">Sancti Fridiani</orgName>,
                        qui est de suppotestatem ipsius <rs key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs>
                        vestro <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>, quas <persName>quondam <name ref="Helpulo"
                                >Ilpulo</name></persName> ad manus suas abuit; casa vero ipsa cum
                        fundamento et edeficio suo, seo curte, orto terris, vineis, silvis,
                        virgareis, pratis, pascuis, cultas res vel incultas, omnia quantum (…) .
                        Obbligo: tali ordinem ut ego vel meis heredes in ipsa casa residere et
                        abitare debeamus et tam ipsa casa quam et predicta res (…) bene laborare et
                        gubernare seo meliorare debeamus nobis privatum fruendum (…). Censo: pro
                        omni censum et iustitiam exinde tibi vel ad successoribus tuis ad pars
                        ipsius ecclesie Sancti Fridiani per singulos annos, per omnem mense
                        decembrio, censum vobis reddere debeamus ad ipsa ecclesia Sancti Fridiani
                        vobis vel ad misso vestro argentum denarios bonos expendiviles numero
                        viginti et sex; et a mandato vestro venire hic Luca legem et iustitiam
                        faciendum tantum (…). Pena: spondeo ego qui supra Auriperto una cum meis
                        heredes conponere tibi (…) argentum soledos viginti (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name ref="Andreas"
                            >Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Churches #Mother_churches #Bishops"
                            >Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ghisulfus">Ghisolfo</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudaldus"
                            >Teudaldus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ermefredus">Ermifridi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Stefanus">Stefanus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
